            <p>Welcome to Sachet Nagarik, your gateway to informed and engaged citizenship in Pokhara Metro!</p>
            <div class="mission">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>At Sachet Nagarik, we are dedicated to fostering civic engagement and empowering the residents of Pokhara Metro with transparent, accessible, and actionable information. Our goal is to bridge the gap between citizens and the local government, ensuring that your voice is heard and your concerns are addressed.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="what-we-do">
                <h2>What We Do</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Online Petitions:</strong> Create and sign petitions on issues that matter to you and your community. Drive change by rallying support and bringing attention to important causes.</li>
                    <li><strong>Complaints:</strong> Report local issues and problems directly through our platform. Whether it's road maintenance, waste management, or public safety concerns, your complaints will be forwarded to the relevant authorities for resolution.</li>
                    <li><strong>Queries:</strong> Have a question about local governance, projects, or services? Submit your queries, and we'll provide you with accurate and timely information.</li>
                    <li><strong>Polls:</strong> Participate in polls to voice your opinions on various topics. Your feedback will help shape community decisions and policies.</li>
                    <li><strong>Community Events:</strong> Stay informed about upcoming community events and activities. Participate in local initiatives, volunteer opportunities, and public meetings to stay engaged and involved.</li>
                </ul>
